Snipcart,is,a,service,that,lets,users,add,a,shopping,cart,to,their,website,The,cart,can,be,customized,using,HTML,and,CSS,to,make,it,match,the,site,s,design,Snipcart,is,also,capable,of,adapting,to,the,customer,s,screen,size,allowing,it,to,work,just,as,well,on,mobile,devices,as,PCs,Snipcart,can,perform,payment,processing,shipping,estimates,and,order,management,functions,all,without,taking,the,customer,away,from,the,user,s,website,Developers,can,manage,information,on,orders,customers,and,discounts,using,the,Snipcart,API